summary: Okay but what if TJ and Kira’s matching is accidental? So Cyrus and TJ plan the salt and pepper costume but at the last minute...
body: Okay but what if TJ and Kira’s matching is accidental? So Cyrus and TJ plan the salt and pepper costume but at the last minute Cyrus backs out so he won’t hurt Andi’s feelings. TJ comes to school in his typical “I play basketball” attire and he happens to match with Kira who probably shamelessly owns a million clothes with basketball things all over it. Plus they’re not exact matches. They have different fonts so it could possibly be a coincidence that they have similar shirts.
